#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.46"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.46:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.46:0.2"
msgid "5. Rohitassavagga"
msgstr "5. With Rohitassa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.46:0.3"
msgid "46. Dutiyarohitassasutta"
msgstr "46. With Rohitassa (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.46:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then, when the night had passed, the Buddha addressed the mendicants:"

msgctxt "an4.46:1.2"
msgid ""
"“imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ rohitasso devaputto abhikkantāya rattiyā "
"abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho, "
"bhikkhave, rohitasso devaputto maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""
"“Tonight, the glorious god Rohitassa, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, "
"came to me, bowed, stood to one side, and said to me:"

msgctxt "an4.46:1.3"
msgid ""
"‘yattha nu kho, bhante, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na "
"upapajjati, sakkā nu kho so, bhante, gamanena lokassa anto ñātuṃ vā daṭṭhuṃ "
"vā pāpuṇituṃ vā’ti?"
msgstr ""
"‘Sir, is it possible to know or see or reach the end of the world by "
"traveling to a place where there’s no being born, growing old, dying, "
"passing away, or being reborn?’ …"

msgctxt "an4.46:1.4"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, bhikkhave, rohitassaṃ devaputtaṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"(The rest of this discourse is the same as the previous discourse, AN 4.45.)"

msgctxt "an4.46:1.5"
msgid ""
"‘yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, "
"nāhaṃ taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:1.6"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bhikkhave, rohitasso devaputto maṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:1.7"
msgid "‘acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:1.8"
msgid "Yāva subhāsitamidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:1.9"
msgid ""
"yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, "
"nāhaṃ taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmi’."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.50"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.46:2.1"
msgid ""
"Bhūtapubbāhaṃ, bhante, rohitasso nāma isi ahosiṃ bhojaputto iddhimā "
"vehāsaṅgamo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:2.2"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpo javo ahosi, seyyathāpi nāma daḷhadhammā "
"dhanuggaho sikkhito katahattho katūpāsano lahukena asanena appakasirena "
"tiriyaṃ tālacchāyaṃ atipāteyya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:2.3"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpo padavītihāro ahosi, seyyathāpi nāma puratthimā "
"samuddā pacchimo samuddo."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:2.4"
msgid ""
"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhante, evarūpena javena samannāgatassa evarūpena ca "
"padavītihārena evarūpaṃ icchāgataṃ uppajji:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:2.5"
msgid "‘ahaṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ pāpuṇissāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:2.6"
msgid ""
"So kho ahaṃ, bhante, aññatreva asitapītakhāyitasāyitā aññatra "
"uccārapassāvakammā aññatra niddākilamathapaṭivinodanā vassasatāyuko "
"vassasatajīvī vassasataṃ gantvā appatvāva lokassa antaṃ antarāyeva kālaṅkato."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.46:3.1"
msgid "Acchariyaṃ, bhante, abbhutaṃ, bhante."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:3.2"
msgid "Yāva subhāsitamidaṃ, bhante, bhagavatā:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:3.3"
msgid ""
"‘yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, "
"nāhaṃ taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:3.4"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, ahaṃ, bhikkhave, rohitassaṃ devaputtaṃ etadavocaṃ:"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.46:4.1"
msgid ""
"‘Yattha kho, āvuso, na jāyati na jīyati na mīyati na cavati na upapajjati, "
"nāhaṃ, taṃ gamanena lokassa antaṃ ñāteyyaṃ daṭṭheyyaṃ patteyyanti vadāmī’ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:4.2"
msgid "Na cāhaṃ, āvuso, appatvāva lokassa antaṃ dukkhassantakiriyaṃ vadāmi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.46:4.3"
msgid ""
"Api cāhaṃ, āvuso, imasmiṃyeva byāmamatte kaḷevare sasaññimhi samanake "
"lokañca paññāpemi lokasamudayañca lokanirodhañca lokanirodhagāminiñca "
"paṭipadanti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.46:5.1"
msgid "Gamanena na pattabbo,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.46:5.2"
msgid "lokassanto kudācanaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.46:5.3"
msgid "Na ca appatvā lokantaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.46:5.4"
msgid "dukkhā atthi pamocanaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.46:6.1"
msgid "Tasmā have lokavidū sumedho,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.46:6.2"
msgid "Lokantagū vusitabrahmacariyo;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.46:6.3"
msgid "Lokassa antaṃ samitāvi ñatvā,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.46:6.4"
msgid "Nāsīsatī lokamimaṃ parañcā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.46:6.5"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
